This fork has been modified and extended by the ElasticDash team.

- Fork Repository: https://github.com/[your-org]/elasticdash-python
- Modifications Copyright: Copyright (c) 2024-2026 ElasticDash
- License: MIT License (same as original)

## Key Differences from Langfuse

ElasticDash extends the original Langfuse SDK with:

- Custom observability features for the ElasticDash platform
- Integration with ElasticDash Logger (https://logger.elasticdash.com)
- Additional instrumentation and monitoring capabilities
- Enhanced OpenTelemetry integration
- Support for additional LLM providers and frameworks

